Package gov.nasa.pds.harvest.search.oodt.filemgr

Class XmlRpcStructFactory

java.lang.Object
gov.nasa.pds.harvest.search.oodt.filemgr.XmlRpcStructFactory
public final class XmlRpcStructFactory extends Object
Version:
$Revision$

A factory class for creating File Manager structures suitable for transfer over the XML-RPC pipe, and for reading objects from the XML-RPC pipe into File Manager structs.

Author:
mattmann, bfoster
